            "chapterTitle": "Prohibition of Show-off",
            "urn": 1624180,
            "body": "<p>Abu Hurairah (May Allah be pleased with him) said: The Messenger of Allah (\ufdfa) said, \"Almighty Allah says, 'I am the One Who is most free from want of partners. He who does a thing for the sake of someone else beside Me, I discard him and his polytheism..\"<br/><br/><b>[Muslim]</b>.<br/><br/></p>",
